{"article_id":"LbCurB2J5HSIAGEH","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"A majority of Americans support background checks ,","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"but the process has been criticized by many .","depth":2},{"id":2,"text":"Background checks :","depth":3},{"id":3,"text":"Do they work ?","depth":3},{"id":4,"text":"The federal background check system for gun buyers is porous , ineffective , and hampered by a lack of cooperation from the states .","depth":4},{"id":5,"text":"For critics , it ' s much more than that .","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"They warn","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"that","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"even if the system can be perfected","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"- and there ' s growing consensus in Washington , D.C. ,","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"that the time has come","depth":11},{"id":11,"text":"to authorize certain basic and largely non-controversial improvements -","depth":11},{"id":12,"text":"it will do nothing","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"to reduce gun violence .","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"President Barack Obama called on Congress to implement universal background checks as part of the gun-control proposals","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"he unveiled in the wake of the Dec. 14 shooting at Sandy Hook Elementary School in Newtown , Conn. ,","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"where 20 children and six others were killed .","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"\" It ' s time for Congress to require a universal background check for anyone","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"trying to buy a gun , \"","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"Obama said .","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"\" If you want to buy a gun","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"- whether it ' s from a licensed dealer or a private seller -","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"you should at least have to show","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"you are not a felon or somebody legally prohibited from buying one .","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"This is common sense . \"","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"Recent polling indicates","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"that nearly everybody agrees","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"- a CBS/New York Times poll put support for universal background checks at 92 percent ,","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"including 85 percent among those","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"living in a household with an National Rifle Association member .","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"Even Sen. Joe Manchin","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"( D-W.V . ) ,","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"a hunter and gun rights advocate","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"who has an \" A \" rating from the NRA ,","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"said on Thursday","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"that he was working with lawmakers","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"- and the NRA -","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"on a bill","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"to update and improve the check system .","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"\" I ' m working on a bill right now with other senators","depth":12},{"id":40,"text":"- Democrats and Republicans -","depth":12},{"id":41,"text":"we ' re trying to get it ,","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"and looking at a background check","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"that basically says","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"that","depth":13},{"id":45,"text":"if you ' re going to be a gun owner ,","depth":15},{"id":46,"text":"you should be able to pass a background check","depth":15},{"id":47,"text":"to be able to get that , with exceptions , \"","depth":14},{"id":48,"text":"Manchin told the MetroNews station in West Virginia .","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"\" I ' m working with the NRA ,","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"to be honest with you ,","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"and talking to them . \"","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"The effort","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"to repair the system","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"stems from widespread agreement","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"that it ' s rendered nearly useless","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"because of two key problems :","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"A giant-sized loophole exists","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"in that some private sellers aren ' t required to do checks ;","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"and many states aren ' t providing the feds with the vital needed information","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"to maintain a meaningful database of those","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"who , legally , have no right","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"to purchase firearms .","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"In particular , this pertains to mental health problems and drug use .","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"\" Most Americans support background checks ,","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"but they ... have very little clue about what that means , \"","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"said David Kopel , a gun law expert and adjunct Constitutional law professor at the University of Denver .","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"\" When you phrase something in an attractive way like ' universal background checks , '","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"who wouldn ' t be for it ?","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"But","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"if you get into the details ,","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"there ' s a bit more grey-area . \"","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"The FBI denied 72,659 attempted gun buys in 2010 ,","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"based on red flags","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"raised by the background check system ,","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"according to the most recent data","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"available from the Department of Justice .","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"That ' s just 1.2 percent of the more than 6 million applications .","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"The most common reasons :","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"nearly half were felony indictment or conviction ;","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"19 percent were fugitives ;","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"and 11 percent were those","depth":12},{"id":82,"text":"who had violated state laws .","depth":12},{"id":83,"text":"The rejection rate has been essentially unchanged over the years .","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"( There is a right","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"to appeal . )","depth":9}],"relations":[{"parent":171,"left":87,"right":170,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":87,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":170,"left":88,"right":169,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":88,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":169,"left":97,"right":168,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":97,"left":4,"right":96,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":96,"left":5,"right":95,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":95,"left":6,"right":94,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":94,"left":7,"right":93,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":93,"left":91,"right":92,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":91,"left":8,"right":90,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":90,"left":9,"right":89,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":89,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":92,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":168,"left":134,"right":167,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":134,"left":107,"right":133,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":107,"left":99,"right":106,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":99,"left":14,"right":98,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":98,"left":15,"right":16,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":106,"left":101,"right":105,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":101,"left":100,"right":19,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":100,"left":17,"right":18,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":105,"left":104,"right":24,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":104,"left":103,"right":23,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":103,"left":102,"right":22,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":102,"left":20,"